headline: T-Mobile US, Inc. to Present at the Goldman Sachs Communacopia + Technology Conference
summary: BELLEVUE, Wash., September 03, 2025--Mike Sievert, president & chief executive officer, and Srini Gopalan, chief operating officer of T-Mobile US, Inc. (NASDAQ: TMUS), will present and provide a business update on Wednesday, September 10, 2025 at 12:25 p.m. Pacific Daylight Time (PDT) at the Goldman Sachs Communacopia + Technology Conference.

headline: Verizon Rises 9.5% Year to Date: Should You Invest in VZ Stock Now?
summary: VZ stock is up 9.5% YTD as it expands fiber, 5G, and new plans, but faces tough competition from AT&T and T-Mobile.
